odal_main_2529465\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lab1665703211298.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lab1665703211298.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lab1665703211298.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lab1665703211298\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies a comma-separated list of plug-in components that can add JavaScript to web pages generated by DSPs and USPs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lab1665703211298__topic_d137864e1_d137865e1_d137866e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lab1665703211298__p_d137867e1_d137868e1_d137869e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>\n<sup class=\"ph sup\">1 </sup>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>\n<sup class=\"ph sup\">n</sup>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lab1665703211298__section_o3x_rxd_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d677341e78\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lab1665703211298__table_w1628ab1b5b3b3b1_w1629ab1b5b3b3_w1630ab1b5b3_w1631ab1b5_w1632ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vcm1665702739978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vcm1665702739978.html\" title=\"Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the $logical ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals.\">[LOGICALS]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lab1665703211298__section_y43_sxd_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d677341e137\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lab1665703211298__p_d137876e1_d137877e1_d137878e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>—name of a component to be activated by Uniface when\n        assembling a response to a browser request for a DSP or USP. If multiple components are\n        specified, they must be separated by commas.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lab1665703211298__section_cgn_sxd_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d677341e149\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lab1665703211298__p_d137882e1_d137883e1_d137884e1\">An output filter is a component that processes data\n        sent by the server to the client.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"lab1665703211298__example_aqq_zxd_vvb\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lab1665703211298__p_d137885e1_d137886e1_d137887e1\">For example, If you create a web output filter called\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">PerformanceFilter</code> add it to the application configuration:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"lab1665703211298__pre_bqq_zxd_vvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[LOGICALS]\nUWEBOUTPUTFILTERS=PerformanceFilter</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/urh1665702755394.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in</a><p>Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529465\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529465\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies a comma-separated list of plug-in components that can add JavaScript to web pages generated by DSPs and USPs. UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS = ComponentName 1 { , ComponentName n } Defaults Assignment file: Application assignment file Section: [LOGICALS] Default value: None Arguments ComponentName —name of a component to be activated by Uniface when assembling a response to a browser request for a DSP or USP. If multiple components are specified, they must be separated by commas. Description An output filter is a component that processes data sent by the server to the client. For example, If you create a web output filter called PerformanceFilter add it to the application configuration: [LOGICALS] UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS=PerformanceFilter Copy Related Links Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}